$$\widehat{OR}=\frac{\widehat{p_1}/(1-\widehat{p_1})}{\widehat{p_2}/(1-\widehat{p_2})}= \dfrac{0.3722/(1-0.3722)}{0.1131/(1-0.1131)}= 4.6499$$

